import React from 'react';
import Navbar from './Navbar'
import NavItems from './NavItems'
import NavItem from './NavItem'

import Container from './Container.js'

import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route, Link } from 'react-router-dom'


import Stats from './Stats.js'
import RP from './RP.js'
import Combat from './Combat.js'
import Bag from './Bag.js'

class Play extends React.Component {
	render() { return (
		<Router>
	    <Container>
	    	<Navbar>
	    		<NavItems justify='center'>
	    			<NavItem><Link to='/play/stats'>Stats</Link></NavItem>
	    			<NavItem><Link to='/play/rp'>RP</Link></NavItem>
	    			<NavItem><Link to='/play/combat'>Combat</Link></NavItem>
	    			<NavItem><Link to='/play/bag'>Bag</Link></NavItem>
	    		</NavItems>
	    	</Navbar>
	    	<Container>

	    	</Container>


	        <Switch>
	          	<Route path="/stats">
		           <Stats />
	          	</Route>
	          	<Route path="/rp">
		            <RP />
	          	</Route>
	          	<Route path="/combat">
			        <Combat />
	          	</Route>
	          	<Route path="/bag">
			        <Bag />
	          	</Route>	          	
	        </Switch>	 
    	</Container>
    	</Router>		
	);}
}

export default Play;
